premise_source_doc_sentence: The drug nitroglycerin  (  GTN  )  is a formulation of the same chemical substance used as the explosive nitroglycerin .

For over 130 years , nitroglycerin has been used medically as a potent vasodilator  (  dilation of the vascular system  )  to treat heart conditions , such as angina pectoris and chronic heart failure .
